reviewText: This is a very good dvd with some unbeatable cartoons. MUCH better then that trash they show today. Popeye is on it, he beats the tar out of Bluto a lot. Baby Huey stars in a cartoon called QUACK-A-DOODLE-DOO! It has Peeping Penguins plus another cartoon called Pinic Panic which stars a gang of singing teapots! AND SO MANY MORE!
